staging: comedi: ni_mio_cs: use comedi_pcmcia_{enable, disable}

Use the comedi_pcmcia_{enable,disable} helpers to enable/disable
the PCMCIA device.

This driver uses a local (*conf_check) to check the pcmcia_device
configuration.

